snippet.title: Dicey Bugs - Trailer
snippet.description:
➤Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3438640/Dicey_Bugs/
➤Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/xWxN6CVTbP

Dicey Bugs is a roguelike, turn-based deckbuilder where you control both sides of the battle, using strategy to shape the outcome of each turn. Catch cute bugs, customize your dice, and unlock abilities to build powerful synergies as you roll your way to victory!
